node.text:
So much more than a hypercar: #C10 represents a ‘classic’ experience defined in new ways.

It is the essence of the purest Pagani spirit, where one of the guiding elements in the creation of our cars has always been Leonardo da Vinci’s principle of Art and Science. Da Vinci taught us that it is possible to marry art and science, though it takes a lot of time and sacrifice to do so. 

A new journey is beginning, guided by state-of-the-art technology and the joy of driving.

#Pagani #WorldPremiere

A spark, a line, a thrill.

We are about to write a new chapter in our story, a celebration and affirmation of the vision which has always been our inspiration: to dream big and strive every day to improve, pursuing our ideals and harnessing our passion to bring them to life.

#C10: a new authentic experience is coming

#Pagani #WorldPremiere

Monterey, what a wonder!

The melody of the Pagani V12 engine accompanied the last two days of #MontereyCarWeek, giving us unforgettable moments. We cannot describe the adrenaline rush of the circuit and the thrill of tackling #LagunaSeca aboard real technological gems, but we can let you relive it!

Catching up with all our friends from North America was the icing on the cake!

#Pagani #HuayraR #ZondaRevolucion

The celebration of the ""Year of the R"".
Yesterday the star was the latest member of the Pagani family: the #HuayraR.

The sculpted in performance hypercar made its US debut bewitching Laguna Seca, during the Rolex Monterey Motorsports Reunion.
Enjoy its Pagani V12-R sound!

But this is just a taste...today we are again ready to hit the track!

#Pagani #MontereyCarWeek #LagunaSeca #Huayra
